## Installation

### Method 1: Via `skills` package (recommended)

Requires [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) 18+ and the `skills` npm package (v1.5.12+).

```bash
npx skills install {{SKILL_AUTHOR}}/{{SKILL_NAME}}
```

### Method 2: Manual clone

```bash
git clone https://github.com/{{SKILL_AUTHOR}}/{{SKILL_NAME}}.git ~/.claude/skills/{{SKILL_NAME}}
```

